project3.three
Class LocationsAndValue

java.lang.Object
  project3.three.Locations
      project3.three.LocationsAndValue

public class LocationsAndValue
extends Locations

For every variable in a predicate list we need to store the locations of where that variable appears (there can be more than one) and store the value for the variable. 

 Domain Definition:
     locations : Set<Location> -- the locations where a variable appears
     value     : Constant      -- the value for the variable

 Instance Invariant:
     locations ≠ null
Last Modified: 21 Feb 2006
